   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>On Pachon 23, has brought Patermouthis son of Dioskoros, of the village of Karanis, of the fourth indiction, two-hundred and forty litrai of chaff, 240 litrai, only. (I,) Isara, (have signed).</ab>
